    <sect4>
     <!-- 
 <title>Server Settings</title>
 -->
 <title>服务器设置</title>

     <itemizedlist>

      <listitem>
       <!--
<para>
        Greatly reduce System V <link linkend="sysvipc">shared
        memory</link> requirements (Robert Haas)
       </para>
-->
<para>
大大的减少了System V <link linkend="sysvipc">共享内存</link>的需求 (Robert Haas)
