       </para>
-->
<para>
配置参数<varname>unix_socket_directory</>被
<link linkend="guc-unix-socket-directories"><varname>unix_socket_directories</></link>
取代，它接受一个路径列表。
</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
       <!--
<para>
        Allow a directory of configuration files to be processed (Magnus
        Hagander, Greg Smith, Selena Deckelmann)
       </para>
-->
<para>
允许配置文件的路径被处理 (Magnus Hagander, Greg Smith, Selena Deckelmann)
</para>

       <!--
<para>
        Such a directory is specified with <link
        linkend="config-includes"><varname>include_dir</></link> in the server
        configuration file.
       </para>
-->
<para>
这样一个路径在服务器配置文件中用
<link linkend="config-includes"><varname>include_dir</></link>指定。
</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
       <!--
<para>
        Increase the maximum <link
        linkend="APP-INITDB">initdb</link>-configured value for <link
        linkend="guc-shared-buffers"><varname>shared_buffers</></link>
        to 128MB (Robert Haas)
       </para>
-->
<para>
为<link linkend="guc-shared-buffers"><varname>shared_buffers</></link>
增加最大<link linkend="APP-INITDB">initdb</link>配置值到128MB (Robert Haas)
</para>

       <!--
<para>
        This is the maximum value that initdb will attempt to set in <link
        linkend="config-setting-configuration-file"><filename>postgresql.conf</></link>;
        the previous maximum was 32MB.
       </para>
-->
<para>
这是initdb打算在<link linkend="config-setting-configuration-file"><filename>postgresql.conf</></link>
中设置的最大值；以前的最大值是32MB。
</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
       <!--
<para>
        Remove the <link linkend="guc-external-pid-file">external
        <acronym>PID</> file</link>, if any, on postmaster exit
        (Peter Eisentraut)
       </para>
-->
<para>
在主进程退出时，删除<link linkend="guc-external-pid-file">外部<acronym>PID</>文件</link>，
如果有 (Peter Eisentraut)
</para>
      </listitem>

     </itemizedlist>

    </sect4>

   </sect3>

   <sect3>
    <!-- 
<title>Replication and Recovery</title>
-->
<title>复制和恢复</title>

     <itemizedlist>

      <listitem>
       <!--
<para>
        Allow a streaming replication standby to <link
        linkend="protocol-replication">follow a timeline switch</link>
        (Heikki Linnakangas)
       </para>
-->
<para>
允许流复制备用<link linkend="protocol-replication">遵循时间线切换</link> (Heikki Linnakangas)
</para>

       <!--
<para>
        This allows streaming standby servers to receive WAL data from a slave
        newly promoted to master status.  Previously, other standbys would
        require a resync to begin following the new master.
       </para>
-->
<para>
这允许流备用服务器从一个新晋升为主要地位的伺服接受WAL数据。以前，
其他备用会请求重新同步以开始跟随新的主机。
</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
       <!--
<para>
        Add <acronym>SQL</> functions <link
        linkend="functions-admin-backup"><function>pg_is_in_backup()</></link>
        and <link
        linkend="functions-admin-backup"><function>pg_backup_start_time()</></link>
        (Gilles Darold)
       </para>
-->
<para>
添加<acronym>SQL</>函数<link linkend="functions-admin-backup"><function>pg_is_in_backup()</></link>
和<link linkend="functions-admin-backup"><function>pg_backup_start_time()</></link> 
(Gilles Darold)
</para>

       <!--
<para>
        These functions report the status of base backups.
       </para>
-->
<para>
这些函数报告基础备份的状态。
</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
       <!--
<para>
        Improve performance of streaming log shipping with <link
        linkend="guc-synchronous-commit"><varname>synchronous_commit</></link>
        disabled (Andres Freund)
       </para>
-->
<para>
提高<link linkend="guc-synchronous-commit"><varname>synchronous_commit</></link>
禁用时流日志切换的性能 (Andres Freund)
</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
       <!--
<para>
        Allow much faster promotion of a streaming standby to primary (Simon
        Riggs, Kyotaro Horiguchi)
       </para>
-->
<para>
允许更快的晋升流备用为主服务器 (Simon Riggs, Kyotaro Horiguchi)
</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
       <!--
<para>
        Add the last checkpoint's redo location to <link
        linkend="APP-PGCONTROLDATA"><application>pg_controldata</></link>'s
        output (Fujii Masao)
       </para>
-->
<para>
添加最后检查点的重做位置到
<link linkend="APP-PGCONTROLDATA"><application>pg_controldata</></link>
的输出 (Fujii Masao)
</para>

       <!--
<para>
        This information is useful for determining which <acronym>WAL</>
        files are needed for restore.
       </para>
-->
<para>
这个信息对于确定恢复需要哪个<acronym>WAL</>文件是有帮助的。
</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
       <!--
<para>
        Allow tools like <link
        linkend="app-pgreceivexlog"><application>pg_receivexlog</></link>
        to run on computers with different architectures (Heikki
        Linnakangas)
       </para>
-->
<para>
允许像<link linkend="app-pgreceivexlog"><application>pg_receivexlog</></link>
这样的工具用不同的架构在计算机上运行 (Heikki Linnakangas)
</para>

       <!--
<para>
        WAL files can still only be replayed on servers with the same
        architecture as the primary; but they can now be transmitted to and
        stored on machines of any architecture, since the
        streaming replication protocol is now machine-independent.
       </para>
-->
<para>
WAL文件仍然只能以原先相同的架构在服务器上重放；但是他们现在可以以任意架构在机器上传输和存储，
因为流复制协议现在是与机器无关的。
</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
       <!--
<para>
        Make <link
        linkend="app-pgbasebackup"><application>pg_basebackup</></link>
        <option>-&#045;write-recovery-conf</> output a
        minimal <filename>recovery.conf</> file (Zolt&aacute;n
        B&ouml;sz&ouml;rm&eacute;nyi, Magnus Hagander)
       </para>
-->
<para>
让<link linkend="app-pgbasebackup"><application>pg_basebackup</></link> 
<option>--write-recovery-conf</>输出一个最小的<filename>recovery.conf</>文件
(Zolt&aacute;n B&ouml;sz&ouml;rm&eacute;nyi, Magnus Hagander)
</para>

       <!--
<para>
        This simplifies setting up a standby server.
       </para>
-->
<para>
这简化了设置一个备用服务器。
</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
       <!--
<para>
        Allow <link
        linkend="app-pgreceivexlog"><application>pg_receivexlog</></link>
        and <link
        linkend="app-pgbasebackup"><application>pg_basebackup</></link>
        <option>-&#045;xlog-method</> to handle streaming timeline switches
        (Heikki Linnakangas)
       </para>
-->
<para>
允许<link linkend="app-pgreceivexlog"><application>pg_receivexlog</></link>
和<link linkend="app-pgbasebackup"><application>pg_basebackup</></link> 
<option>--xlog-method</>处理流时间线切换 (Heikki Linnakangas)
</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
       <!--
<para>
        Add <link
        linkend="guc-wal-receiver-timeout"><varname>wal_receiver_timeout</></link>
        parameter to control the <acronym>WAL</> receiver's timeout
        (Amit Kapila)
       </para>
-->
<para>
添加<link linkend="guc-wal-receiver-timeout"><varname>wal_receiver_timeout</></link>
参数控制<acronym>WAL</>接收器的超时 (Amit Kapila)
</para>

       <!--
<para>
        This allows more rapid detection of connection failure.
       </para>
-->
<para>
这允许更快速的检测连接失败。
</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
       <!--
<para>
        Change the <link linkend="wal"><acronym>WAL</></link> record format to
        allow splitting the record header across pages (Heikki Linnakangas)
       </para>
-->
<para>
改变<link linkend="wal"><acronym>WAL</></link>记录格式，
以允许跨页面分离记录头 (Heikki Linnakangas)
</para>

       <!--
<para>
        The new format is slightly more compact, and is more efficient to
        write.
       </para>
-->
<para>
新的格式更紧凑，并且书写更有效。
</para>
      </listitem>

     </itemizedlist>

   </sect3>

   <sect3>
    <!--
<title>Queries</title>
-->
<title>查询</title>

     <itemizedlist>

      <listitem>
       <!--
<para>
        Implement <acronym>SQL</>-standard <link
        linkend="queries-lateral"><literal>LATERAL</></link> option for
        <literal>FROM</>-clause subqueries and function calls (Tom Lane)
       </para>
