       </para>
-->
<para>
如果给定的初始值字符串对于事务数据类型来说不是有效的输入，
那么让<link linkend="sql-createaggregate"><command>CREATE AGGREGATE</></link>
投诉 (Tom Lane)
</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
       <!--
<para>
        Suppress <link linkend="SQL-CREATETABLE"><command>CREATE
        TABLE</></link>'s messages about implicit index and sequence creation
