       </para>
-->
<para>
抑制<link linkend="SQL-CREATETABLE"><command>CREATE TABLE</></link>
关于隐式索引和序列创建的消息 (Robert Haas)
</para>

       <!--
<para>
        These messages now appear at <literal>DEBUG1</> verbosity, so that
