      <listitem>
       <!--
<para>
        Allow <application>pgbench</> to aggregate performance statistics
        and produce output every <option>-&#045;aggregate-interval</>
        seconds (Tomas Vondra)
       </para>
-->
<para>
允许<application>pgbench</>集合性能统计和每<option>--aggregate-interval</>
秒产生输出 (Tomas Vondra)
</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
       <!--
<para>
        Add <application>pgbench</> <option>-&#045;sampling-rate</> option
        to control the percentage of transactions logged (Tomas Vondra)
       </para>
-->
<para>
添加<application>pgbench</> <option>--sampling-rate</>选项，
控制事务日志的百分比 (Tomas Vondra)
</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
       <!--
<para>
        Reduce and improve the status message output of
        <application>pgbench</>'s initialization mode (Robert Haas,
        Peter Eisentraut)
       </para>
-->
<para>
减少并改进<application>pgbench</>的初始化模式的状态消息输出 (Robert Haas, Peter Eisentraut)
</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
       <!--
<para>
        Add <application>pgbench</> <option>-q</> mode to print one output
        line every five seconds (Tomas Vondra)
       </para>
-->
<para>
添加<application>pgbench</> <option>-q</>模式，每5秒打印一行输出 (Tomas Vondra)
</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
       <!--
<para>
        Output <application>pgbench</> elapsed and estimated remaining
        time during initialization (Tomas Vondra)
       </para>
-->
<para>
在初始化期间输出<application>pgbench</>经过和预估的剩余时间 (Tomas Vondra)
</para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
       <!--
<para>
        Allow <application>pgbench</> to use much larger scale factors,
        by changing relevant columns from <type>integer</> to <type>bigint</>
